pageTitle: Passing the torch; Torrey Smith takes over dad's realty company | SentinelNews.com
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {21074=Starting Jan. 1, Torrey took ownership of the real estate firm W. A. has owned since 1979. At the same time, the company is regaining its independence.
